highlights.text: “PASSO BEM SOLTO - Slowed” by ATLXS has been on Viral Songs South Korea the longest, at 159 days straight.
HANRORO has the most spots on Viral Songs South Korea. “Goodbye, My Summer” is the highest at #16.
“ACELERADA” by sma$her and MXZI is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs South Korea, up 53 spots at #47.
